text: Kutashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Lemez-Tamaksky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 361 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 1 km from Lemez-Tamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Kutashevo
